@startuml
title Microwave Oven Control - State Diagram

[*] --> Idle

state "Idle" as Idle {
  entry / Display current time
  do / Wait for user input
}

state "WaitingForInput" as WaitingForInput {
  entry / Display power level options and cooking time prompt
  do / Get user input
  exit / Start cooking or cancel
}

state "Cooking" as Cooking {
  entry / Start cooking process at selected power level
  do / Monitor cooking time
  exit / Stop cooking if door is opened or timer expires
}

state "DoorOpen" as DoorOpen {
  entry / Stop cooking process
  do / Return to idle state
}

state "Stopped" as Stopped {
  entry / Display current time
  do / Wait for next use
}

Idle --> WaitingForInput : User selects power level or enters cooking time

WaitingForInput --> Cooking : Power selected and cooking time entered
WaitingForInput --> Idle : Cancelled

Cooking --> DoorOpen : Door opened during cooking process
Cooking --> Stopped : Timer expired or user cancels

DoorOpen --> Idle : Door closed

Stopped --> Idle : Next use

@enduml
